(ns o2w.routes
  (:require [accountant.core :as accountant]
            [bide.core :as bide :refer [router match]]
            [o2w.routes.helpers :refer [prevent-reload-on-known-path]]
            [reagent.core :as r]
            [goog.events :as events]
            [goog.history.EventType :as EventType]
            [clojure.string :as str]))

(def app-routes (r/atom [[]]))
(def app-views (r/atom {}))
(def current-route (r/atom {}))
(def default-view (r/atom nil))
(def -default-language (r/atom nil))
(def language (r/atom nil))
(def -language? (r/atom true))
(defn ->slash [s] (str/replace s #"--slash--" "/"))
(defn slash-> [s] (str/replace s #"/" "--slash--"))
(def query (r/reaction (->> (:query @current-route)
                            (map (fn [[k v]] [(subs (str k) 1) v]))
                            (into {}))))

(def confirm? (r/atom nil))

(defn cms-routes [routes k]
  (->> routes
       (map (fn [i] [(str "/" i) k]))
       (into [])))

(defn process-params [params]
  (let [params   (or params {})
        current  (or @language @-default-language)
        params   (merge {:language current} params)
        default? (= (:language params) @-default-language)]

    (cond-> params
      (or default? (not @-language?)) (dissoc :language))))

(defn url [name & [params query]]
  (let [params' (process-params params)]
    (bide/resolve @app-routes name params' query)))

(defn go [path & params] (accountant/navigate! (apply url path params)))

(defn url-for [{:keys [name params query]} language]
  (url name (merge params {:language language}) query))

(defn add-i18n [prefix routes]
  (->> routes
       (map (fn [[route k]] [(str "/:language(" prefix ")" route) k]))
       (into [])))

(def add-l18n add-i18n)

(defn with-prefix [prefix routes]
  (->> routes
       (map (fn [[route k]] [(str prefix route) k]))
       (into [])))

(defn- default-nav-handler [{:keys [router on-change default-language on-change-language language?]} path navigation?]
  (let [[path hash]                  (str/split path #"#")
        [handler route-params query] (match @router path)
        default-params               {:language default-language}
        route-params                 (merge default-params route-params)
        current-language             (keyword (:language route-params))]

    (reset! current-route {:path        path
                           :name        handler
                           :params      route-params
                           :hash        hash
                           :query       query
                           :navigation? navigation?})

    (when (and @-language? (not (= @language current-language)))
      (let [old @language]
        (reset! language current-language)
        (when on-change-language (on-change-language current-language old))))

    (when (and (not navigation?) on-change) (on-change @current-route))))

(defn- default-path-exists? [routes path] (match @routes path))

(defn- parse-routes [_routes views]
  (if views
    [_routes views]
    (let [routes (->> _routes (map #(vector (first %) (second %))) (into []))
          views  (->> _routes (map #(hash-map (second %) (last %))) (into {}))]
      [routes views])))

(defn confirm-route-change [nav-handler token navigation?]
  (.replaceState js/window.history {} nil (:path @current-route))
  (@confirm? #(do
                (.replaceState js/window.history {} nil token)
                (nav-handler token navigation?))))

(defn- dispatch-on-navigate
  [history nav-handler]
  (events/listen
    history
    EventType/NAVIGATE
    (fn [e]
      (let [token       (.-token e)
            navigation? (.-isNavigation e)]

        (if @confirm?
          (confirm-route-change nav-handler token navigation?)
          (nav-handler token navigation?))))))

(defn configure-navigation!
  [{:keys [nav-handler path-exists? reload-same-path?]}]
  (.setUseFragment accountant/history false)
  (.setPathPrefix accountant/history "")
  (.setEnabled accountant/history true)
  (set! accountant/nav-handler nav-handler)
  (set! accountant/path-exists? path-exists?)
  (dispatch-on-navigate accountant/history nav-handler)
  (prevent-reload-on-known-path accountant/history path-exists? reload-same-path?))

(defn on-navigate [name params query]
  (reset! current-route {:name   name
                         :params params
                         :query  query}))

(defn start!
  "Configura las rutas de la app"
  [{:keys [routes nav-handler path-exists? not-found on-change views
           default-language on-change-language language?]
    :or   {nav-handler  default-nav-handler
           path-exists? default-path-exists?
           language?    true}}]

  (reset! -default-language default-language)
  (reset! -language? language?)
  (when not-found (reset! default-view not-found))

  (let [[routes views] (parse-routes routes views)]
    (reset! app-routes (router routes))
    (reset! app-views views)
    (configure-navigation! {:nav-handler  (partial nav-handler {:router             app-routes
                                                                :on-change          on-change
                                                                :on-change-language on-change-language
                                                                :default-language   default-language})
                            :path-exists? (partial path-exists? app-routes)})
    (accountant/dispatch-current!)))

(defn current-view []
  (let [{:keys [path name params query]} @current-route
        handler                          (get @app-views name)]

    (when path
      (cond
        handler       [handler @current-route params query]
        @default-view [@default-view @current-route params query]))))
